HEADWORD: Drawgear
<hw>Draw"gear`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
harness for draught horses.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Railroad)</fld> <def>The means or parts by which
